name: SwapFish
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.
The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en: SwapFish Finance is a Decentralized Exchange protocol native to the Arbitrum blockchain. With SwapFish users can trade crypto assets as well as earn trading fees and FISH tokens. FISH token is a governance and utility token native to the SwapFish ecosystem. FISH token distribution will begin with emissions to liquidity providers on SwapFish and single staking pool as seen on Pancakeswap and other popular swaps. During the protocol development we will aim to bring more utility to FISH token holders in the form of revenue sharing and voting.
